{"tid":1681034,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭將於本周四赴上海及南京 下周二晚返港","createTime":"2019-10-29T07:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T07:59:53.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ba217b31bf9d389d947e09883ea3cd31f0d481d8","tid":1681034,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:14:01.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥將於本月31日前往上海，出席「香港節2019──藝匯上海」和相關活動，以及下星期舉行的第二屆中國國際進口博覽會。林鄭月娥亦會在11月2日及3日訪問南京，出席第二屆蘇港融合發展峰會並致辭，以及見證香港貿易發展局與江蘇省簽署第七次蘇港合作聯席會議紀要和其他項目。政制及內地事務局長聶德權和民政事務局長劉江華將會參與部分行程。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥將於11月5日晚上返港，她離港期間，由政務司長張建宗署理特首職務。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191029/s00001/1572332454209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191029%2Fs00001%2F1572332454209%2F&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg25ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=68489be5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191029%2Fs00001%2F1572332454209%2F&h=cbd3fc52\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191029/s00001/1572332454209/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />走咁多日"},{"pid":"331326d7fe4457657b6ab8740dcbfcab30a8d02f","tid":1681034,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:14:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jc8536k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJc8536k.jpg&h=6d7fb408&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a317bab13cbefdff0f1fb8226b12b5a7211461fc","tid":1681034,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:15:15.000Z","msg":"去咁撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595a7c31e2bdb73983b557e0071013efdc226b31","tid":1681034,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:16:26.000Z","msg":"又順便見韓正?"},{"pid":"bf77e